56:34.258 --> 56:36.225
Why is this guy so desperate?

56:36.327 --> 56:38.160
- How well do you know this guy?

56:38.262 --> 56:39.461
- Not very well.

56:39.563 --> 56:41.697
Our assistant, she
made the introduction

56:41.799 --> 56:42.898
between Tony and Brent,

56:43.000 --> 56:44.800
but I didn't have
anything to do with it.

56:46.103 --> 56:47.002
- Sounds fishy.

56:47.104 --> 56:49.138
- No, Brent wouldn't go there.

56:49.240 --> 56:50.239
- But he did.

56:51.909 --> 56:53.342
- Steve, no.

56:53.444 --> 56:54.843
- I think it's
time we take a look

56:54.945 --> 56:56.578
into Brent's
financial activities.

57:08.125 --> 57:09.158
- You've
reached Brent Gould.

57:09.260 --> 57:10.159
Leave me a message.

57:10.261 --> 57:11.493
- I don't want this over.

57:14.098 --> 57:15.731
