telling what I'll do.

57:52.169 --> 57:53.235
- I don't understand

57:53.337 --> 57:54.570
why he doesn't keep this
stuff at the office.

57:54.672 --> 57:56.238
- He's paranoid
about our employees

57:56.340 --> 57:58.941
