59:04.475 --> 59:06.608
or he's hiding something.

59:06.710 --> 59:08.043
- No, he,

59:08.145 --> 59:09.144
he trusts me.

59:09.246 --> 59:10.612
I have access to everything.

59:10.714 --> 59:12.047
Here look.

59:13.317 --> 59:15.250
Here's our agreement
