59:33.270 --> 59:35.370
This is not what we agreed on.

59:35.472 --> 59:36.872
- Who's this company again?

59:38.509 --> 59:40.309
- M & G Holdings.
- M & G Holdings.

59:40.411 --> 59:42.044
- I don't know much about them.

59:43.414 --> 59:45.247
There's not that much on the
internet about them, either.

59:45.349 --> 59:47.349
They don't even have a website.

59:47.451 --> 59:49.785
- See if there's any owners
of the company listed.

59:52.990 --> 59:54.823
- No, nothing.

59:54.925 --> 59:56.959
Just a P.O. Box in Delaware.

59:58.429 --> 59:59.695
It's not unusual.

01:00:03.634 --> 01:00:04.833
- You know what?

01:00:04.935 --> 01:00:06.702
My partner joined the
